<div class="container-fluid">
	<div class="row paddingExtra">
		<div class="col-md-8">
			<div id="header">
				<img class="animated slideInLeft" src="/img/aperture-xxl.png">
				<h1>Theia</h1>
		</div>
			<p id="about">It's as easy as creating an account and uploading an image. Theia will detect one or more human faces
				and provide data visualization for face attributes using machine learning-based predictions of facial features.
				See examples below for more information.
			</p>
			<i id="downArrow" class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-4x" aria-hidden="true" onclick="window.location.hash='exampleRow';"></i>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<div class="try">
				<h3 id="animated" class="animated tada">Give it a try without signing in!</h3>
				<p>Upload your photo here to see Theia in action.</p>
				<%if(currentUser){%>
					<form enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/profile/" method="post">
	          <input type="file" name="myFile">
	          <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
	        </form>
				<%}else{%>
				<form enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/" method="post">
					<input type="file" name="myFile">
					<input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
				</form>
			<%}%>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row text-center exampleRow">
		<div class="col-md-3">
			<div class="icons">
				<i class="fa fa-users fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
			</div>
			<h4>Demographics</h4>
			<p>Displays perceived age and gender.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
			<div class="icons">
				<i class="fa fa-smile-o fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
			</div>
			<h4>Emotions</h4>
			<p>Visualizes machine learning-based predictions of displayed emotions.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
			<div class="icons">
				<img src="/img/color.png">
			</div>
			<h4>Hair Color</h4>
			<p>Presents predictions of hair color.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
			<div class="icons">
				<img src="/img/moustache.png">
			</div>
			<h4>Icons</h4>
			<p>Displays icons to represent smiling, glasses and facial hair.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" id="howItWorks">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<h4>How it works</h4>
			<p>Theia uses the <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/cognitive-services/face/Microsoft">Microsoft Face API</a> to detect one or more human faces in an image.
				It provides the coordinates of the face, along with face attributes which contain machine learning-based predictions of facial features.
				Microsoft uses the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viola%E2%80%93Jones_object_detection_framework">Viola-Jones object detection framework</a>.
				Theia displays information received from the Microsoft Face API using user-friendly, interactive charts and other data visualization techniques.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- woman eating salad example -->
	<div class="row padding exampleRow">
		<h4> Theia will display perceived gender, age, emotions and hair color. </h4>
	</div>
	<div class="row exampleRow paddingBottom">
		<div class="col-offset-md-1 col-md-6 text-center">
			<img class="try inputImage imageBorder" src="/img/examples/saladImg.png">
			<div class="exampleDemo">
				<img class="demographics" src="/img/examples/saladDemo.png">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<div id="myExampleCarousel" class="carousel slide">
				<ol class="carousel-indicators">
					<li data-target="#myExampleCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
					<li data-target="#myExampleCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
				</ol>
				<div class="carousel-inner">
					<div class="item active">
						<div class="chart-container">
								 <img data-animation="animated bounceInDown" src="/img/examples/saladEmotions.png">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="item">
						<div class="chart-container">
								 <img data-animation="animated bounceInDown" src="/img/examples/saladHair.png">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a class="left carousel-control" href="#myExampleCarousel" data-slide="prev">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" style="color:#F2C777"></span>
					<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
				</a>
				<a class="right carousel-control" href="#myExampleCarousel" data-slide="next">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" style="color:#F2C777"></span>
					<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- harold -->
	<div class="row padding exampleRowPink">
		<div class="col-md-12">
		<h4> Theia analyzes for seven different emotions: anger, contempt, disgust, fear, neutral, happiness, sadness and surprise. </h4>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row exampleRowPink paddingBottom">
		<div class="col-offset-md-1 col-md-6 text-center">
			<img class="try inputImage" src="/img/examples/haroldImg.png">
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6 charts text-center">
			<img class="try inputImage" src="/img/examples/haroldEmotions.png">
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- group example -->
	<div class="row padding exampleRow">
		<h4> Theia can recognize and provide data for up to six faces at a time. </h4>
	</div>
	<div class="row exampleRow paddingBottom">
		<div class="col-offset-md-1 col-md-6 text-center">
			<img class="try inputImage imageBorder" src="/img/examples/womanImg.png">
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6 charts text-center">
			<img class="tryPink inputImage" src="/img/examples/womanEmotionsChart.png">
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
